  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add onions and garlic to the pan. Sauté until translucent, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add sliced bell peppers and sauté for another minute.",
    "Stir in ground szechuan peppercorns and fresh ginger. Cook for an additional 1-2 minutes.",
    "Pour in lime juice and mix well.",
    "Toss kale with the vegetables, cooking until just wilted but still crisp, about 3-5 minutes.",
    "Season with sea salt to taste."
